WEBVTT

00:06.560 --> 00:08.189
Listen, if you're having
any second thoughts,

00:08.260 --> 00:10.290
you want to call this off,
now is the time.

00:13.100 --> 00:15.800
I don't want
to call it off.

00:17.600 --> 00:20.300
So no "We're going
anywhere" last looks.

00:20.370 --> 00:24.370
No tears, no "I'll miss you
most of all, Scarecrow."

00:24.440 --> 00:26.340
Nothing that anybody
can look back on.

00:26.410 --> 00:28.210
Look, I know
how to play my part.

00:28.280 --> 00:31.150
After you force me
to open up the safe,

00:31.220 --> 00:32.650
you can't go straight
for the cash box.

00:32.720 --> 00:34.520
You got to grab some
of the other shit, too.

00:34.580 --> 00:35.520
Yeah? Like what?

00:35.590 --> 00:37.350
Anything.

00:37.420 --> 00:39.720
It can't look like
you got tipped off

00:39.790 --> 00:40.860
what to take.

00:40.920 --> 00:43.460
Take the cash box last.

00:43.530 --> 00:46.630
That'll be my signal
to go for the shotgun.

00:48.060 --> 00:50.100
I'll try not to fire.

00:52.270 --> 00:53.700
You know
how adrenaline can be.

00:53.770 --> 00:55.940
Yeah, well, you won't
get a shot off,

00:56.010 --> 00:57.540
but thanks
for the concern.

00:57.610 --> 00:58.640
You just worry about

00:58.710 --> 01:00.940
making it all look
good for the camera

01:01.010 --> 01:03.150
and making sure
you're alone.

01:03.180 --> 01:05.180
I'll be alone.

