40:56.970 --> 40:59.670
That must have been
cute as hell.

40:59.740 --> 41:01.380
But yeah,
she lost the lisp.

41:01.440 --> 41:04.710
She grew into a beautiful,
smart woman.

41:05.580 --> 41:07.450
Look, I know

41:07.550 --> 41:09.720
