I'll let you call Audrey,

41:42.920 --> 41:45.290
- and you can be the hero.
- Yeah, absolutely not.

41:45.350 --> 41:46.650
You're
not coming with me,

41:46.720 --> 41:48.920
and I'm not giving
you the money.

41:48.990 --> 41:51.030
Hey. Hey.

41:52.890 --> 41:54.900
I'm the only one with
the combination to the safe.

41:54.960 --> 41:57.930
