any brilliant ideas

42:05.970 --> 42:07.640
about following me,
either.

42:15.620 --> 42:16.750
Come on.

42:56.060 --> 42:57.760
Shut the fuck up.
Shut the fuck up.

42:57.830 --> 43:00.090
