I swear to Christ

43:00.160 --> 43:02.730
I'll bury this in your
fucking Adam's apple.

43:07.940 --> 43:09.940
I'm here to cut you loose.

43:18.080 --> 43:21.220
Now this gag.
Don't test me.

43:36.160 --> 43:37.100
Uhh!

43:57.790 --> 43:59.750
Moved your car around back.

43:59.820 --> 44:01.860
Uh-uh. My gun.

44:01.920 --> 44:04.530
Not going to happen.

44:04.590 --> 44:05.990
Katie's got it,

44:06.060 --> 44:07.730
so if you don't
want to get shot,

44:07.800 --> 44:09.300
don't wake her up.

44:12.770 --> 44:14.140
Detective.

44:15.770 --> 44:17.810
Me and my family
ain't going anywhere.

44:17.870 --> 44:19.840
This is our home.

44:19.910 --> 44:21.910
I see you around here again,

44:21.980 --> 44:23.810
I'm gonna assume the worst,

44:23.880 --> 44:26.010
cop or no cop.

44:29.250 --> 44:32.390
There's nothing I won't do
to protect my family.

44:32.450 --> 44:34.860
Tell me you understand that.

44:36.460 --> 44:38.660
I understand.

44:38.760 --> 44:40.090
I hope so.

44:48.800 --> 44:50.240
We're closed.

44:56.310 --> 44:57.780
You can't be here.

44:57.780 --> 44:59.080
I told you over the phone.

44:59.150 --> 45:00.950
Sean's due back
from Hartford any minute.

45:02.620 --> 45:04.150
Taylor.

45:11.160 --> 45:13.460
I was out
at Reading Road today.

45:15.800 --> 45:17.100
Taylor, I can't.

45:17.160 --> 45:18.470
You know, they woke up
that morning,

45:18.530 --> 45:20.000
just like any other day.

45:21.370 --> 45:23.840
Drank their coffee,
brushed their teeth.

45:23.910 --> 45:27.070
Dropped Carly off
at kindergarten,

45:27.140 --> 45:29.480
never knowing
they were doing it all

45:29.540 --> 45:30.950
for the last time.

45:33.480 --> 45:35.880
You think they thought
of any of that?

45:37.420 --> 45:38.420
That moment when they--

45:38.490 --> 45:40.450
when they saw the pickup
blow the stop sign?

45:43.660 --> 45:46.830
Because I'm--
I'm wondering...

45:46.860 --> 45:49.500
if maybe there's--
there's no such thing

45:49.560 --> 45:51.100
as never knew
what hit them.

45:51.170 --> 45:53.000
Maybe that's just
something you say

45:53.070 --> 45:56.070
on next of kin
notification.

45:56.140 --> 45:57.870
You know?

45:57.940 --> 46:01.240
I'm wondering
if there isn't--

46:01.310 --> 46:03.980
there isn't
always a moment...

46:05.480 --> 46:07.180
when you look back

46:07.250 --> 46:11.550
and you see all the
things that you did...

46:14.020 --> 46:16.360
and all the things
that you didn't do.

46:16.420 --> 46:17.390
Listen, I--

46:18.690 --> 46:20.760
I want to hear this,
I really do, but--

46:20.860 --> 46:23.870
Sean, he's coming
back from Hartford.

46:26.600 --> 46:28.000
A couple of months ago,

46:28.070 --> 46:30.070
