of not being a cop--

46:30.140 --> 46:31.770
Fuck.

46:31.870 --> 46:33.540
Fuck. He's here.

46:33.610 --> 46:35.680
Taylor, you have to go.

46:35.740 --> 46:37.210
You should be with me.

46:38.480 --> 46:39.780
Not Sean.

46:39.880 --> 46:42.450
I should have said it
in high school.

46:42.520 --> 46:45.050
