on the day he proposed,

46:45.120 --> 46:47.120
but I'm saying it now.

46:48.490 --> 46:49.790
What the fuck is this?

46:49.890 --> 46:51.560
This, fucko,
is me telling you

46:51.630 --> 46:52.990
