telling her.

46:53.060 --> 46:55.030
You keep parking your
fucking monster truck

46:55.100 --> 46:56.700
in front of our place,

46:56.760 --> 46:58.100
I'm going to personally
see to it

46:58.170 --> 47:00.030
that a couple of hoppers
from Marina Village Projects

47:00.100 --> 47:02.300
joy ride it down to one of
the Stratford Ave. cop shops

47:02.370 --> 47:05.040
and turn it into a fucking
art exhibit.

47:07.740 --> 47:10.610
My, Grandma couldn't
handle her own dirty work.

47:10.680 --> 47:12.480
Had to send the cop.

47:12.550 --> 47:15.920
I'll do what I can,
but we get so busy here,

47:15.920 --> 47:17.150
