47:25.330 --> 47:27.160
Oh, you just lost your temper?

47:27.230 --> 47:29.200
You flew off the handle?

47:33.230 --> 47:36.600
Well, I heard you've been
doing that a lot lately.

47:38.740 --> 47:40.140
Hey, if you, uh...

47:40.210 --> 47:41.810
