a guy's nose off.

48:20.250 --> 48:21.680
He's not the kind
of person you forget.

48:21.750 --> 48:22.820
Fuck.

48:22.880 --> 48:24.990
I guess Dockery
got it in his head

48:24.990 --> 48:26.990
