give me the bag?

49:33.250 --> 49:35.090
You can watch me
through the window.

49:36.460 --> 49:39.260
No. I told you we're
doing this together.

50:13.930 --> 50:15.630
Where's that toilet?

50:16.700 --> 50:18.470
Uh...

